            <property name="styleSheet">
             <string notr="true">QLabel {
    color: rgb(80,80,80); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", "Roboto", sans-serif;
}</string>
            </property>
            <property name="text">
             <string>CE HIGH FREQUENCY RESPONSE

── Mode: Given Rπ, Rµ directly ──
Plug Rπ and Rµ straight into the cutoff formulas.

── Mode: Full Circuit ──
RXX = rπ + (β+1)·RX
RSB = RS || RB
RCL = RC || RL
Rπ = rπ(RSB + RX) / (RSB + RXX)
Rµ = [RXX(RSB + RCL) + (β+1)·RSB·RCL] / (RSB + RXX)

── Both modes ──
fπ = 1 / (2π·Rπ·Cπ)
fµ = 1 / (2π·Rµ·Cµ)

fπ || fµ  ≤  fH  ≤  min(fπ, fµ)
Conservative estimate:  fH = fπ || fµ</string>
            </property>
